        <p>Camilla Morton is <em>"the perfect Girl for All Seasons: a ray of sunshine to brighten up a bleak autumn's day, a touch of warmth bought to a cold winter.  She is as welcome as a beautiful springtime bunch of flowers, and a refreshing tonic on a hot summer's day.  That, for me, is Camilla."</em> <strong>Manolo Blahník</strong></p>
